IMO these dungeons are ALOT more 'real' than any other zone in the game. If for no other reasons for the lack of respawns.<br>
<br>
The layout of these dungeons is persistant, the types of mobs in them is persistant, and they have the additional bonus of having persistant content for 2 hours (as opposed to mobs magically appearing again when they respawn).<br>
<br>
To me they seem much more 'real' than the standard dungeons =)<br>
